<scenario>
The agent A provided the following violation scenario:
In lfs_file_rewind, err is assigned from LFS_LOCK(lfs->cfg), and LFS_LOCK is defined as ((void)cfg,0), so err is always 0. Therefore the condition if (err) { return err; } can never be true and the return statement inside that branch is unreachable. This constitutes unreachable code in the project (violation of MISRA C 2023 Rule 2.1).
</scenario>
